      <description>

&lt;h3 id=&#34;award&#34;&gt;Award&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://tobinproject.org/research-inquiry/inequality/2018prize&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Tobin Project 2018 Prize for Exemplary Work on Inequality and Decision Making&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;h3 id=&#34;press&#34;&gt;Press&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
